ORANGE ANGEL FOOD TORTE

¾	cup sugar 
6	tbsp. cornstarch 1 cup water 
1	cup orange juice 1/s top. salt 
2	egg yolks 
	Grated rind ½ orange 
1	tbsp. lemon juice 1 tbsp. butter or margarine 

Mix sugar and cornstarch; gradually add water and strained orange juice. Stir constantly while cooking until smooth and thickened. Cook 3 minutes. Add to slightly beaten egg yolks, return to low heat and cook 2 minutes. Add orange rind, lemon juice and butter. Cool. 

Cut Merita Angel Food Cake in wedge slices. Pour sauce on top. Garnish with orange sections. (Serves 10-12)